1) Adding your query to a hibernate mapping file using the `&lt;sql-query&gt;` tag

    &lt;sql-query name=&quot;MyQuery&quot;&gt;.......

2) Define a hibernate config file that includes the above file using the `&lt;mapping&gt;` tag

